WEBVTT

00:00:01.500 --> 00:00:02.566
Three years ago.

00:00:03.166 --> 00:00:04.500
I was wrong about you.

00:00:04.966 --> 00:00:05.600
Master Lu

00:00:05.700 --> 00:00:09.100
Now is the time to have a good chat about what happened 3 years ago

00:00:09.400 --> 00:00:12.033
You built me into the villa 3 years ago

00:00:12.133 --> 00:00:14.800
It is decided that I am a woman who loves money

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:18.266
Even guess that I approached you for money

00:00:19.066 --> 00:00:21.600
So arrogant you chose to leave without saying goodbye

00:00:21.700 --> 00:00:22.666
I was right.

00:00:22.766 --> 00:00:25.400
Lin Xinmo, I'm already in good shape

00:00:25.500 --> 00:00:26.800
Why can't you forgive me?

00:00:26.900 --> 00:00:29.000
You are always so self-righteous

00:00:29.100 --> 00:00:30.900
Even if you are wrong

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:33.466
You will also ask the world to change for you

00:00:33.566 --> 00:00:36.533
I refuse to condescend and say sorry

00:00:37.366 --> 00:00:40.700
Then why do you think I will forgive you?

00:00:41.900 --> 00:00:44.700
What if I said I was wrong?

00:00:48.066 --> 00:00:49.100
Will you forgive me?

00:00:49.200 --> 00:00:52.100
Will we go back to where we were?

00:00:55.800 --> 00:00:56.766
I will forgive you.

00:00:56.866 --> 00:00:58.200
But we can't go back

00:00:58.300 --> 00:01:00.333
Why? Because

00:01:01.300 --> 00:01:03.366
I have a boyfriend now.